9.02	The_Big_Time	The Big Time	The Big Time (1957) is a short science fiction novel by Fritz Leiber. It won the Hugo Award in 1958. The Big Time is a vast, cosmic back story, hidden behind a claustrophobic front story with only a few characters.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2e/FLBigTime.jpg/200px-FLBigTime.jpg
